{"tid":2339147,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黎智英保釋｜日媒對黎智英獲釋感意外 多國傳媒：壹傳媒是新聞自由關鍵堡壘","createTime":"2020-12-24T12:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T04:51:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"88ec134bf0d168fed84fc7f63a11782ffc7a4fc9","tid":2339147,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_zzCfbt1tFYNN_rIODW2xJwA0tQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TYXCLTMRSVBWFAHS2BJDJLW7SY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_zzCfbt1tFYNN_rIODW2xJwA0tQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTYXCLTMRSVBWFAHS2BJDJLW7SY.jpg&h=85a99c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被控違反報館地契及勾結外國勢力，還柙候審，昨向高等法院申請保釋獲批。美國、英國、日本等多國主流傳媒跟進報道，有報道對黎智英獲准保釋感「意外」，側面反映本港民主派人士面對的艱難困境。<br />\n<br />\n《日經新聞》以「香港出版人黎智英意外地獲准保釋」為題，並引述英國風險管理公司「A2 Global Risk」指，高院准黎保釋的決定挑戰「北京利用香港司法制度打壓示威和異議的意圖」，認為北京不太可能接受法院的裁決，因為裁決未能展示北京對香港以及其司法系統的絕對權威，但「這將進一步危及香港法律體系，而這體系是其作為國際重要金融和貿易中心的基礎」。《日經》又引述「A2 Global Risk」周三在每日客戶報告的分析，預計中國會趁聖誕國際傳媒忙於過節、反應較平時冷淡時，出手「糾正」法院的裁決。<br />\n<br />\n美國多個電視台及報章亦有報道黎智英獲准保釋。其中《紐約郵報》形容黎智英的壹傳媒集團「被視為是其中一個僅餘且關鍵的新聞自由堡壘」，報道亦有指，西方和人權組織一直讉責香港國安法是當局打壓不同政見者的工具。<br />\n<br />\n除了美、英等西方國家傳媒，半島電視台（Al Jazeera）也形容壹傳媒集團是新聞自由其中一個最後陣地，並形容黎智英是其中一個最受北京嚴厲打壓的人士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201224/WCWPXZMNFZFXFEFWHU7NLVRS5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201224%2FWCWPXZMNFZFXFEFWHU7NLVRS5Y%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt4gDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=ad81b0fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201224%2FWCWPXZMNFZFXFEFWHU7NLVRS5Y%2F&h=3f406132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201224/WCWPXZMNFZFXFEFWHU7NLVRS5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"0faf7182b6b914215f38ff26764f390364a7a757","tid":2339147,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b049b9c2e70cdc435979ea5859d76110a8de38c7","tid":2339147,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06c584efac3828cede60281c7c8aad55e24ebca8","tid":2339147,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b049b9c2e70cdc435979ea5859d76110a8de38c7","tid":2339147,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a45031c202a4cd7e9b17196b1c1e46478bb2d46","tid":2339147,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"大波驊上訴至終審法院，可能又會....."},{"pid":"c9d5a4f6fdd68d89320bb3747a8ad7044940e32f","tid":2339147,"uid":305767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41805fd90860875731960617b661f1a5a471d271","tid":2339147,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9d5a4f6fdd68d89320bb3747a8ad7044940e32f","tid":2339147,"uid":305767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img s